body:
@Akhilsnaik Yes we can check the logs to find the Exception stacktrace. However, this change is just to print the Exception message and not the stacktrace. Also, I encountered exception only when I tried changing runAllDBChecks() for some of our requirements some time back and hence, I realized if we have just message available in console, it might be sometimes more useful.

This is not a critical change but just to improve the readability of console error message.
